      <strong>username:</strong> <code>Demo-1</code> and
      <strong>password:</strong> <code>Demo-1</code> <br />
      or create your own user via <a href="/signup">Sign up</a> form <br />
      (no email conformation needed)
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

